sequenceDiagram
    participant EV as event.cpp key or text or paste
    participant DF as dispatch_form_text_replace
    participant BI as editing_dispatch_form_beforeinput
    participant TE as te_replace_byte_range_no_events
    participant TC as tc_set_value
    participant H as te_history_push
    participant V as te_validate
    participant RP as relayout and repaint

    EV->>DF: resolve EditingSurface text control
    DF->>BI: fire cancellable beforeinput
    BI-->>DF: prevented then abort mutation
    DF->>TE: apply UTF-8 byte range replacement
    TE->>TC: write current_value and mirror to form.value
    TC->>H: push value plus selection snapshot to ring
    TC->>V: re-evaluate constraint validation
    TE->>TE: place caret and clear selection and sync projection
    DF->>BI: editing_dispatch_form_input fires input event
    TE->>RP: mutation invalidates layout and paint
